data.description: 4 bedrooms and 3 full bath ranch home located in an established community within the Parkview district. Situated on a large level lot which includes a stocked koi pond & a storage shed. New flooring and fresh paint throughout. The Primary suite and 1 secondary bedroom offer walk-in closets. Unwind in the fireside family room, The separate laundry room is off the kitchen with an exterior entry that can serve as a mud room. Partial basement with a boat door and parking pad. The entertainment deck provides a view of the large backyard. This home is conveniently located to shopping, Stone Mountain Park, and No HOA. Being sold as-is.
